properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 20 at 1:55PM EST until February 22 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 5 to 8 feet expected.

* WHERE...Gulf waters from the Walton-Okaloosa County line to
Apalachicola out 60 nautical miles.

* WHEN...From 6 PM this evening to 9 AM CST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO 9 AM CST SATURDAY
